{"_id":"00skd1kllk1dks00","name":"Marionettes’ Destroyer","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","scenarioSlug":"of-flesh-and-wood","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"141","contentKey":"scenario-gift.of-flesh-and-wood.marionettes-destroyer","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":4,"folderName":"Of Flesh and Wood","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Destructor de marionetas","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> derrotar a cualquier marioneta o comprender que son almas encarceladas en contra de su voluntad.</p><p>Sabes cómo calmar a los espíritus inquietos dándoles una bienvenida adecuada cuando su alma se libera. No te afecta el don Furia sin límites. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional al defenderte de seres animados o controlados por espíritus o magia.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Of Flesh and Wood","requirements":"derrotar a cualquier marioneta o comprender que son almas encarceladas en contra de su voluntad.","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood"},"scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"145"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Defeat any Marionette or understand that they are souls imprisoned against their will.</p><p>You know how to calm restless spirits by giving them a proper greeting when their soul is freed. You are not affected by the Boundless Rage Gift. Receive 1 Additional Success when defending against beings that are animated or controlled by spirits or magic.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Of Flesh and Wood","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Of Flesh and Wood","source":"Of Flesh and Wood","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.of-flesh-and-wood.marionettes-destroyer","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","scenarioSlug":"of-flesh-and-wood","sourceDirectory":"of-flesh-and-wood","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Defeat any Marionette or understand that they are souls imprisoned against their will.","limitations":""},"sort":400000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086874,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00xal7mxxm7lax00","name":"A True Friend","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","scenarioSlug":"of-flesh-and-wood","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"141","contentKey":"scenario-gift.of-flesh-and-wood.a-true-friend","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":5,"folderName":"Of Flesh and Wood","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Amigo verdadero","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> ganarse la confianza de Carlo a pesar de todas sus mentiras.</p><p>Carlo entiende que puede confiar en ti y correrá en tu ayuda si lo necesitas. Puedes gastar 1 Soma para que Carlo aparezca en la escena como PNJ aliado. Utilizará el poder de sus mentiras para ayudarte lo mejor que pueda.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Of Flesh and Wood","requirements":"ganarse la confianza de Carlo a pesar de todas sus mentiras.","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood"},"scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"145"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Gain Carlo’s trust despite all his lies.</p><p>Carlo understands that he can trust you and will run to your aid if you need it. You can spend 1 Soma to have Carlo appear in the Scene as your NPC ally. Carlo will use the power of his lies to help you to the best of his ability.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Of Flesh and Wood","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Of Flesh and Wood","source":"Of Flesh and Wood","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.of-flesh-and-wood.a-true-friend","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","scenarioSlug":"of-flesh-and-wood","sourceDirectory":"of-flesh-and-wood","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Gain Carlo’s trust despite all his lies.","limitations":""},"sort":500000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00lpa2prrp2apl00","name":"The Field of Miracles (Special Gift for The Fox and the Cat)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","scenarioSlug":"of-flesh-and-wood","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"141","contentKey":"scenario-gift.of-flesh-and-wood.the-field-of-miracles","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":6,"folderName":"Of Flesh and Wood","specialFor":"The Fox and the Cat","translations":{"es":{"name":"Campo de los Milagros (don especial para el Zorro y el Gato)","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> llegar a Sinalunga.</p><p>Conoces bien Sinalunga porque es donde se encuentra uno de tus refugios secretos. Una vez por escena puedes gastar 1 Soma para que tú u otro sujeto podáis abandonar la escena y esconderos en el Campo de los Milagros. Nadie puede encontrar la ubicación exacta del refugio. Cuando estés en el Campo, una vez por sesión, puedes recuperar 1 Herida.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Of Flesh and Wood","requirements":"llegar a Sinalunga.","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood"},"scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"145"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Arrive in Sinalunga.</p><p>You know Sinalunga well because it is where one of your secret shelters is located. Once per Scene you can spend 1 Soma so you or another subject can leave the Scene and hide in the Field of Miracles. No one can find the exact location of the shelter. When you are at the Field, once per Session you can recover 1 Wound you have suffered.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Of Flesh and Wood","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Of Flesh and Wood","source":"Of Flesh and Wood","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.of-flesh-and-wood.the-field-of-miracles","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","scenarioSlug":"of-flesh-and-wood","sourceDirectory":"of-flesh-and-wood","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Arrive in Sinalunga.","limitations":""},"sort":600000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
